            </svg> 
           </picture> <h4 class="h-c-headline h-c-headline--four h-has-bottom-margin"> Do more with Google Cloud.</h4> <p class="h-has-bottom-margin"> You can use Google Marketing Platform together with Google Cloud to unlock advanced marketing use cases like building predictive models to get new insights to improve marketing performance.</p> 
           <div class="highlights-module__cta"> <a data-g-event="for enterprises" data-g-action="cloud" data-g-label="learn more" href="/about/resources/meeting-the-data-challenge-with-google-marketing-platform-and-google-cloud/" class="h-c-button h-c-button--primary" title="Learn more">Learn more</a> 
